Search<T> - Interface in codes.algorithms
Interface Search, is implemented in class Algorithms which is used to search the element in the array in sorted and unsorted arrays using Linear Search technique and Binary Search technique.
SingleDimension<T> - Interface in codes.arrays
Interface SingleDimension, is implemented in class ArrayConvertor which is used to convert the multidimensional arrays into single dimension.
Sort<T> - Interface in codes.algorithms
Interface Sort, is implemented in class Algorithms which is used to sort the elements in the array in ascending and descending order using Bubble Sort technique and Selection Sort technique.
Stack<T> - Interface in codes.algorithms.dataStructures
Interface Stack, is implemented in class LinkedList and is used to take in elements from the first index and remove elements from the last index, basically it works on FILO (First-In-Last-Out) technique.
